articles.title: U19 World Cup final: Defending champions India look to rein in Australia again - Hindustan Times
articles.description: India seniors lost to Australia in the 2023 World Test Championship and ODI World Cup finals, but the juniors hold a 2-0 edge in title battles | Cricket
articles.content: On Sunday, India and Australia will run into each other in a marquee final for the third time in less than a year. There was the World Test Championship final at The Oval in June. Then there was the … [+4849 chars]
